                        <p style="color: #9490b3; margin: 0;">Total revenue increased by 23% compared to the previous quarter, driven by enterprise subscriptions.</p>
                    </ArcadiaCard>
                    <ArcadiaCard Title="Clickable Card" Clickable="true" OnClick="HandleCardClick">
